The citizens of Louisiane await you . 
If necessair , we have hole in levee ready to cut . 
But hold , '' he cried , glancing around him , where is Captain Temple ? I heard that he had come to Louisville from the Cumberland to day . 
Is he not going with you to New Orleans , St . 
Gre ? '' I took up the name involuntarily . 
