And Auguste's face lighted up . 
I awoke with a start , and sat for some minutes trying to collect my scattered senses . 
The sun streamed in at my open door , the birds hopped on the lawn , and the various sounds of the bustling life of the little town came to me from beyond . 
Suddenly , with a glimmering of the mad events of the night , I stood up , walked uncertainly into the back room , and stared at the bed . 
I went back into the outer room my eye wandered from the shattered whiskey bottle , which was still on the floor , to the table littered with Mrs. Temple's letters . 
And there , in the midst of them , lay a note addressed with my name in a big , unformed hand . 
Dear Davy , '' so it ran , I have gone away , I cannot tell you where . 
Some day I will come back and you will forgive me . 
God bless you ! NICK . 
Gre were to prepare the way for an insurrection there . 
